# Materials Directory

This directory contains all materials and shaders used in the Music Room VR project.

## Contents:
- Material assets (.mat files)
- Textures (albedo, normal, metallic, roughness maps)
- Custom shaders

## Guidelines:
1. Use descriptive naming (e.g., "drum_metal_chrome.mat", "cymbal_brass.mat")
2. Organize textures in sets:
   - diffuse/albedo
   - normal
   - metallic/roughness
   - emission (if needed)
3. Keep texture sizes optimized for VR (prefer power of 2 dimensions)
4. Use material instances for variations

## Structure Example:
/Materials
  /DrumKit
    - drum_shell_material.mat
    - cymbal_brass_material.mat
    /Textures
      - drum_shell_albedo.png
      - drum_shell_normal.png
  /Environment
    - wall_material.mat
    - floor_material.mat
